  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Equip a Day Center for Orphans in North Macedonia</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Lighthouse of Hope MK exists to provide care for orphans living in North Macedonia. This project seeks to establish our first day center and family-style group home  - The JOY Home - with clean drinking water, a working septic system, water heater, an on-site kennel for the two therapy dogs, and safety/therapy equipment for the children. With your help, The JOY Home Day Center will be ready to open in August 2020, and will serve 5 special needs orphans, ages 5-12.</narrative>
  </description>
